*[[William Lane Craig|Craig, William Lane]] (2010) ''On Guard'' .
*[[Patrick Madrid|Madrid, Patrick]] and [[Kenneth Hensley|Hensley, Kenneth]] (2010), ''The God''less'' Delusion: A Catholic Challenge to Modern Atheism''. Our Sunday Visitor.

